service.tut.pori.fileservice

Class File

  • java.lang.Object
    • service.tut.pori.fileservice.File

  • public class File
extends java.lang.Object
    Details of a single uploaded file. The saved name (file system name) should not be shown to the user, even though it can be figured out from the URL. The name parameter is the filename used provided when uploading/creating the file.

    XML Example

    <?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="yes"?>
<file>
  <fileId>6460818052639628785</fileId>
  <name>uFBhcYKDiGb2lO1P4MZlr6nTCzpIz7hQ</name>
  <url>http://otula.pori.tut.fi:44446/fs_files/4cd06974-868a-442e-b524-f9a04c4a5f53</url>
</file>

    Optional elements
